title: ESP32S3 AC P
content:
substitutions:
  devicename: climate-p
  upper_devicename: "Climate-P"
  model_name: "Climate"


esphome:
  name: $devicename
  friendly_name: ${upper_devicename}
  comment: ESP32S3 for $model_name
  name_add_mac_suffix: true
  project:
    name: "TaiSEIA-Panasonic.$model_name"
    version: "ESP32S3N" #hardware

external_components:
  - source: github://tsunglung/taixia@master
    components: [ taixia ]
    #refresh: 0s

esp32:
  board: esp32-s3-devkitc-1
  flash_size: 16MB
  framework:
    type: arduino
  

wifi:
  ssid: !secret wifi_ssid
  password: !secret wifi_password

  # Enable fallback hotspot (captive portal) in case wifi connection fails
  ap:
    ssid: ${devicename}
    password: "12345678"

psram:
  mode: octal
  speed: 80MHz

captive_portal:

# Enable logging
logger:
  baud_rate: 0 # disable serial logging;
#  level: VERY_VERBOSE

# Enable Home Assistant API
api:

ota:
  - platform: esphome
  - platform: web_server

web_server:

uart:
  id: uart_taixia
  tx_pin: GPIO2 #pin3 (RX to AC)   A1
  rx_pin: GPIO1 #pin4 (TX from AC) A0
  baud_rate: 9600
  debug:
    direction: BOTH
    
status_led:
  pin:
    number: GPIO48 # Blue LED
    #inverted: True # S3 pro need set True

light:

  - platform: rgb
    name: "RGB LED"
    id: board_rgb_led
    red: led_red
    green: led_green
    blue: led_blue

output:

  - platform: ledc
    id: led_red
    pin: GPIO46
    inverted: true

  - platform: ledc
    id: led_green
    pin: GPIO0
    inverted: true

  - platform: ledc
    id: led_blue
    pin: GPIO45
    inverted: true
    
# optional binary sensor to monitor serial connection:
binary_sensor:
  - platform: status
    name: "Status"

button:
  - platform: safe_mode
    name: Safe Mode Boot
    entity_category: diagnostic
  - platform: restart
    name: "Restart"
  - platform: taixia
    type: airconditioner
    get_info:
      name: "Get Info"

climate:
  - platform: taixia
    name: "Climate"
    supported_modes:
      - COOL
      - HEAT
      - DRY
      - FAN_ONLY
    supported_fan_modes:
      - LOW
      - MEDIUM
      - HIGH
      - AUTO
    supported_swing_modes:
      - VERTICAL
      - HORIZONTAL
      - BOTH
    supported_presets:
      - NONE
      - BOOST
      - ECO
      - ACTIVITY
      - SLEEP
      - AWAY


number:
  - platform: taixia
    type: airconditioner
    off_timer:
      name: "Off Timer"

sensor:
  - platform: wifi_signal
    name: "WiFi Signal"
    update_interval: 60s

  - platform: uptime
    name: "Uptime"
    filters:
      - lambda: return x / 3600;
    unit_of_measurement: "h"
    accuracy_decimals: 1

  - platform: internal_temperature
    name: "ESP32 Temperature"

  - platform: taixia
    type: airconditioner
    temperature_indoor:
      name: "Temperature Indoor"
    temperature_outdoor:
      name: "Temperature Outdoor"
    operating_current:
      name: "Current"
    energy_consumption:
      state_class: total_increasing
      name: "Energy"
    operating_watt:
      name: "Power"

select:
  - platform: taixia
    type: airconditioner
    display_mode:
      name: "Display Mode"

switch:
  - platform: taixia
    type: airconditioner
    power:
      name: "Power Switch"
    beeper:
      name: "Buzzer"
    mildew_proof:
      name: "Mildew Proof"
    self_cleaning:
      name: "Self Cleaning"
      
text_sensor:
  - platform: version
    name: "ESPHome Version"
  - platform: wifi_info
    ip_address:
      name: "IP Address"
  - platform: taixia
    sa_id:
      name: "SA ID"
      id: sa_id
    brand:
      name: "SA Brand"
    model:
      name: "SA Model"
    version:
      name: "SA Version"
    services:
      name: "SA Services"

taixia:
  sa_id: 1
  response_time: 65000

  #version: 2 #for old ac
  
time:
  - platform: homeassistant
    id: homeassistant_time

title: Menu Settings
content:
-- Multi Toggle Hide NameTag & All GUI
-- LocalScript di StarterCharScripts (SPS)
-- By @KitooStudioLite

local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local TweenService = game:GetService("TweenService")
local Lighting = game:GetService("Lighting")
local StarterGui = game:GetService("StarterGui")
local SoundService = game:GetService("SoundService")

local LocalPlayer = Players.LocalPlayer
local PlayerGui = LocalPlayer:WaitForChild("PlayerGui")

-- üîä Suara klik
local ClickSound = Instance.new("Sound")
ClickSound.SoundId = "rbxassetid://9118823106" -- suara klik lembut
ClickSound.Volume = 0.6
ClickSound.Parent = SoundService

-- ‚öôÔ∏è Simpan & Muat Setting
local function SaveSetting(name, state)
	PlayerGui:SetAttribute(name, state)
end

local function LoadSetting(name)
	return PlayerGui:GetAttribute(name)
end

-- üéõÔ∏è GUI Utama
local ScreenGui = Instance.new("ScreenGui")
ScreenGui.Name = "SettingsGUI"
ScreenGui.ResetOnSpawn = false
ScreenGui.IgnoreGuiInset = true
ScreenGui.Parent = PlayerGui

-- ‚öôÔ∏è Tombol Buka Menu
local OpenButton = Instance.new("TextButton")
OpenButton.Size = UDim2.new(0, 38, 0, 38)
OpenButton.Position = UDim2.new(1, -50, 0, 10)
OpenButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(40, 40, 40)
OpenButton.Text = "‚öôÔ∏è"
OpenButton.TextSize = 26
OpenButton.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 255, 255)
OpenButton.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold
OpenButton.Parent = ScreenGui
Instance.new("UICorner", OpenButton).CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 30)

local Shadow = Instance.new("ImageLabel")
Shadow.Size = UDim2.new(1, 12, 1, 12)
Shadow.Position = UDim2.new(0, -6, 0, -6)
Shadow.BackgroundTransparency = 1
Shadow.Image = "rbxassetid://1316045217"
Shadow.ImageTransparency = 0.5
Shadow.ImageColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0, 0, 0)
Shadow.ZIndex = -1
Shadow.Parent = OpenButton

-- üß≠ Frame Menu
local Frame = Instance.new("Frame")
Frame.Size = UDim2.new(0, 240, 0, 260)
Frame.Position = UDim2.new(0.5, -120, 0.5, -130)
Frame.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(25, 25, 25)
Frame.Visible = false
Frame.Parent = ScreenGui
Instance.new("UICorner", Frame).CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 12)

-- Shadow belakang menu
local FrameShadow = Shadow:Clone()
FrameShadow.Size = UDim2.new(1, 20, 1, 20)
FrameShadow.Position = UDim2.new(0, -10, 0, -10)
FrameShadow.ImageTransparency = 0.6
FrameShadow.Parent = Frame

-- üìú ScrollingFrame
local Scroll = Instance.new("ScrollingFrame")
Scroll.Size = UDim2.new(1, -12, 1, -12)
Scroll.Position = UDim2.new(0, 6, 0, 6)
Scroll.CanvasSize = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 400)
Scroll.ScrollBarThickness = 6
Scroll.BackgroundTransparency = 1
Scroll.Parent = Frame

local UIList = Instance.new("UIListLayout")
UIList.Padding = UDim.new(0, 10)
UIList.Parent = Scroll

-- üè∑Ô∏è Judul
local Title = Instance.new("TextLabel")
Title.Text = "‚öôÔ∏è Settings Menu"
Title.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 45)
Title.BackgroundTransparency = 1
Title.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 255, 255)
Title.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold
Title.TextSize = 22
Title.Parent = Scroll

-- üîò Fungsi Buat Toggle
local function CreateToggle(parent, labelText, attributeName, callback)
	local ToggleFrame = Instance.new("Frame")
	ToggleFrame.Size = UDim2.new(1, -20, 0, 45)
	ToggleFrame.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(40, 40, 40)
	ToggleFrame.Parent = parent
	Instance.new("UICorner", ToggleFrame).CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 10)

	local Label = Instance.new("TextLabel")
	Label.Text = labelText
	Label.Size = UDim2.new(0.6, 0, 1, 0)
	Label.Position = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0, 0)
	Label.BackgroundTransparency = 1
	Label.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
	Label.Font = Enum.Font.Gotham
	Label.TextSize = 18
	Label.TextXAlignment = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left
	Label.Parent = ToggleFrame

	local ToggleButton = Instance.new("Frame")
	ToggleButton.Size = UDim2.new(0, 50, 0, 26)
	ToggleButton.Position = UDim2.new(1, -60, 0.5, -13)
	ToggleButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(80, 80, 80)
	ToggleButton.Parent = ToggleFrame
	Instance.new("UICorner", ToggleButton).CornerRadius = UDim.new(1, 0)

	local Knob = Instance.new("Frame")
	Knob.Size = UDim2.new(0, 22, 0, 22)
	Knob.Position = UDim2.new(0, 2, 0, 2)
	Knob.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(200, 200, 200)
	Knob.Parent = ToggleButton
	Instance.new("UICorner", Knob).CornerRadius = UDim.new(1, 0)

	local state = LoadSetting(attributeName) or false

	local function UpdateVisual()
		local color = state and Color3.fromRGB(0, 200, 80) or Color3.fromRGB(80, 80, 80)
		local knobPos = state and UDim2.new(1, -24, 0, 2) or UDim2.new(0, 2, 0, 2)
		TweenService:Create(ToggleButton, TweenInfo.new(0.25), {BackgroundColor3 = color}):Play()
		TweenService:Create(Knob, TweenInfo.new(0.25), {Position = knobPos}):Play()
	end

	UpdateVisual()
	callback(state)

	ToggleButton.InputBegan:Connect(function(input)
		if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch or input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 then
			state = not state
			ClickSound:Play()
			SaveSetting(attributeName, state)
			UpdateVisual()
			callback(state)
		end
	end)
end

-- üéöÔ∏è Dropdown Mode Grafik
local function CreateGraphicsDropdown(parent)
	local FrameG = Instance.new("Frame")
	FrameG.Size = UDim2.new(1, -20, 0, 50)
	FrameG.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(40, 40, 40)
	FrameG.Parent = parent
	Instance.new("UICorner", FrameG).CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 10)

	local Label = Instance.new("TextLabel")
	Label.Text = "Graphics Mode"
	Label.Size = UDim2.new(0.6, 0, 1, 0)
	Label.Position = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0, 0)
	Label.BackgroundTransparency = 1
	Label.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
	Label.Font = Enum.Font.Gotham
	Label.TextSize = 18
	Label.TextXAlignment = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left
	Label.Parent = FrameG

	local Dropdown = Instance.new("TextButton")
	Dropdown.Size = UDim2.new(0.4, -10, 0, 30)
	Dropdown.Position = UDim2.new(0.6, 5, 0.5, -15)
	Dropdown.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(70, 70, 70)
	Dropdown.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
	Dropdown.Text = LoadSetting("GraphicsMode") or "Medium"
	Dropdown.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold
	Dropdown.TextSize = 16
	Dropdown.Parent = FrameG
	Instance.new("UICorner", Dropdown).CornerRadius = UDim.new(1, 0)

	local DropFrame = Instance.new("Frame")
	DropFrame.Size = UDim2.new(1, -20, 0, 90)
	DropFrame.Position = UDim2.new(0, 10, 1, 5)
	DropFrame.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(50, 50, 50)
	DropFrame.Visible = false
	DropFrame.ZIndex = 10
	DropFrame.Parent = FrameG
	Instance.new("UICorner", DropFrame).CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 6)

	local UIList2 = Instance.new("UIListLayout")
	UIList2.Parent = DropFrame

	local modes = {"Low", "Medium", "High"}

	local function ApplyGraphics(mode)
		if mode == "Low" then
			Lighting.GlobalShadows = false
			Lighting.Brightness = 1
			Lighting.FogEnd = 150
		elseif mode == "Medium" then
			Lighting.GlobalShadows = true
			Lighting.Brightness = 2
			Lighting.FogEnd = 300
		elseif mode == "High" then
			Lighting.GlobalShadows = true
			Lighting.Brightness = 3
			Lighting.FogEnd = 800
		end
	end

	local function CreateOption(text)
		local b = Instance.new("TextButton")
		b.Text = text
		b.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 30)
		b.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(70, 70, 70)
		b.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
		b.Font = Enum.Font.Gotham
		b.TextSize = 16
		b.Parent = DropFrame

		b.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
			ClickSound:Play()
			Dropdown.Text = text
			SaveSetting("GraphicsMode", text)
			ApplyGraphics(text)
			DropFrame.Visible = false
		end)
	end

	for _, m in ipairs(modes) do
		CreateOption(m)
	end

	ApplyGraphics(Dropdown.Text)

	Dropdown.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
		ClickSound:Play()
		DropFrame.Visible = not DropFrame.Visible
	end)
end

-- üë§ Hide NameTag
local function SetNameTagsVisible(state)
	for _, plr in pairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
		if plr.Character and plr.Character:FindFirstChild("Head") then
			for _, obj in pairs(plr.Character.Head:GetChildren()) do
				if obj:IsA("BillboardGui") then
					obj.Enabled = state
				end
			end
		end
	end
end

Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(plr)
	plr.CharacterAdded:Connect(function()
		task.wait(1)
		SetNameTagsVisible(not LoadSetting("HideNameTag"))
	end)
end)

-- üß© Hide GUI
local function SetAllGUIVisible(state)
	for _, gui in pairs(PlayerGui:GetChildren()) do
		if gui:IsA("ScreenGui") and gui.Name ~= "SettingsGUI" and gui.Name ~= "TouchGui" then
			gui.Enabled = state
		end
	end
	local touchGui = PlayerGui:FindFirstChild("TouchGui")
	if touchGui then
		touchGui.Enabled = true
	end
	StarterGui:SetCore("TopbarEnabled", state)
	pcall(function() StarterGui:SetCoreGuiEnabled(Enum.CoreGuiType.Chat, state) end)
	pcall(function() StarterGui:SetCoreGuiEnabled(Enum.CoreGuiType.PlayerList, state) end)
	pcall(function() StarterGui:SetCoreGuiEnabled(Enum.CoreGuiType.Backpack, state) end)
end

-- Tambahkan ke Scroll
CreateToggle(Scroll, "Hide NameTags", "HideNameTag", function(state)
	SetNameTagsVisible(not state)
end)

CreateToggle(Scroll, "Hide All GUI", "HideAllGUI", function(state)
	SetAllGUIVisible(not state)
end)

CreateGraphicsDropdown(Scroll)

-- üé¨ Animasi buka/tutup menu
local isOpen = false
OpenButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
	isOpen = not isOpen
	ClickSound:Play()

	if isOpen then
		Frame.Visible = true
		TweenService:Create(Frame, TweenInfo.new(0.3, Enum.EasingStyle.Back), {
			BackgroundTransparency = 0
		}):Play()
	else
		local tween = TweenService:Create(Frame, TweenInfo.new(0.25), {
			BackgroundTransparency = 1
		})
		tween:Play()
		tween.Completed:Wait()
		Frame.Visible = false
	end
end)

title: Dom BRF1
content:
monitor = peripheral.wrap("monitor_1")
function pos(...) return term.setCursorPos(...) end
function cls(...) return term.clear() end
function tCol(...) return term.setTextColor(...) end
function bCol(...) return term.setBackgroundColor(...) end
function box(...) return paintutils.drawFilledBox(...) end
function line(...) return paintutils.drawLine(...) end
function write(...) return term.write(...) end
term.redirect(monitor)
w, h = monitor.getSize()

function getSize() w,h = monitor.getSize() end
tCol(colors.white)
local darkmode = true
local darkmodec

local boolArray = {false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false}

local function brf1()
    monitor.setTextScale(1.5)
    getSize()
    cls()
    if darkmode then
    darkmodec = colours.black
else
    darkmodec = colours.blue
end
    box(1,1,w,h,darkmodec)
    pos(w/2-#"BRF1"/2,1)
    write("BRF1")

    -- left column
    local y = 3
    pos(5,y) write("Asurine")
    if boolArray[1]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Redstone")
    if boolArray[2]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Lapis")
    if boolArray[3]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Quartz")
    if boolArray[4]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Coal")
    if boolArray[5]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Diamond")
    if boolArray[6]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Coal Dust")
    if boolArray[7]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Steel Dust")
    if boolArray[8]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Flint")
    if boolArray[9]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end

    -- right column
    local y2 = 3
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Cobalt")
    if boolArray[10]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end; y2=y2+2
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Ostrum")
    if boolArray[11]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end; y2=y2+2
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Lead")
    if boolArray[12]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end; y2=y2+2
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Desh")
    if boolArray[13]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end; y2=y2+2
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Clay")
    if boolArray[14]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end; y2=y2+2
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Silver")
    if boolArray[15]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end; y2=y2+2
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Ashes")
    if boolArray[16]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end; y2=y2+2
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Iron")
    if boolArray[17]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end

    pos(1,h)
    bCol(colors.black)
    write("EXIT")
    while true do
        local event, button, mx, my = os.pullEvent()
        if event == "monitor_touch" then
            if mx >= 1 and mx <= (1+#"EXIT") and my == h then
                return "menu"
            end
            -- left
            local ly = 3
            for i=1,9 do
                if mx >= 23 and mx <= 26 and my == ly then boolArray[i]=not boolArray[i]; brf1() end
                ly = ly + 2
            end
            -- right
            local ry = 3
            for i=10,17 do
                if mx >= 46 and mx <= 49 and my == ry then boolArray[i]=not boolArray[i]; brf1() end
                ry = ry + 2
            end
            if mx >= w/2-#"BRF1"/2 and mx <= w/2+#"BRF1"/2 and my == 1 then
                darkmode = not darkmode
                brf1()
            end
        end
    end
end

return {brf1 = brf1}

local ReplicatedStorage = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage")
local HttpService = game:GetService("HttpService")
local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local UnitConfig = require(ReplicatedStorage.Databases.UnitConfig)
local BadgeData = require(ReplicatedStorage.Databases.BadgeData)
local GeneralData = require(ReplicatedStorage.Databases.GeneralData)
local Common = require(ReplicatedStorage.Common)
local Sound = require(ReplicatedStorage.Shared.Sound)
local Server = require(ReplicatedStorage.Blink.Server)

local TRADE_TIMEOUT = 120 
local MAX_TRADE_UNITS = 8
local TRADE_COOLDOWN = 5
local TRADE_EXECUTION_DELAY = 5

local function generateTradeId()
	return HttpService:GenerateGUID()
end

local function isValidUnit(unitId, playerData)
	return playerData.Inventory.Units[unitId] ~= nil
end

local function getPlayerInventoryCount(playerData)
	local count = 0
	for _ in pairs(playerData.Inventory.Units) do
		count = count + 1
	end
	return count
end

local function getMaxUnitsForPlayer(playerData)
	local maxUnits = GeneralData.Settings.Default_MaxUnits or 100
	local owned = (playerData and playerData.Gamepasses) or {}
	
	local storagePassBonus = {
		[1462584282] = 50,
		[1462564275] = 50,
		[1298364212] = 50, 
	}
	for passId, bonus in pairs(storagePassBonus) do
		if table.find(owned, passId) then
			maxUnits += bonus
		end
	end
	return maxUnits
end

local function validateInventorySpaceAfterTrade(playerData, unitsToAdd, unitsToGive)
	local addCount, giveCount = 0, 0
	for _ in pairs(unitsToAdd or {}) do addCount += 1 end
	for _ in pairs(unitsToGive or {}) do giveCount += 1 end

	local currentCount = getPlayerInventoryCount(playerData)
	local maxUnits = getMaxUnitsForPlayer(playerData)
	local finalCount = currentCount - giveCount + addCount
	return finalCount <= maxUnits
end

local function validateInventorySpace(playerData, unitsToAdd)
	local currentCount = getPlayerInventoryCount(playerData)
	local maxUnits = GeneralData.Settings.Default_MaxUnits
	if playerData and playerData.Gamepasses then
		if table.find(playerData.Gamepasses, 1298364212) then
			maxUnits = maxUnits + 50
		end
	end
	local unitsToAddCount = 0
	for _ in pairs(unitsToAdd) do
		unitsToAddCount = unitsToAddCount + 1
	end
	return currentCount + unitsToAddCount <= maxUnits
end

local TradingManager = {}
TradingManager.activeTrades = {}
TradingManager.playerCooldowns = {}
TradingManager.tradeRequests = {}

function TradingManager:Init(gameModule)
	self.game = gameModule
	
	Server.SendTradeRequest.On(function(sender, payload)

		local targetUserId
		
		if typeof(payload) == "table" and payload.UserId then
			targetUserId = tonumber(payload.UserId)
		elseif typeof(payload) == "number" then
			local function toSignedI32(n: number): number
				local r = n % 4294967296
				if r >= 2147483648 then
					r -= 4294967296
				end
				return r
			end

			local receivedI32 = payload
			for _, p in ipairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
				if toSignedI32(p.UserId) == receivedI32 then
					targetUserId = p.UserId
					break
				end
			end

			if not targetUserId then
				for _, p in ipairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
				end
				Server.UI.Fire(sender, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Player not found!", 3, "Error"}})
				return
			end
		else
			Server.UI.Fire(sender, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Player not found!", 3, "Error"}})
			return
		end

		return self:SendTradeRequest(sender, targetUserId)
	end)

	Server.AcceptTrade.On(function(player, struct)
		return self:RespondToTradeRequest(player, struct)
	end)

	Server.AddUnitToTrade.On(function(player, struct)
		return self:AddUnitsToTrade(player, struct)
	end)

	Server.RemoveUnitFromTrade.On(function(player, struct)
		return self:RemoveUnitFromTrade(player, struct)
	end)

	Server.ConfirmTrade.On(function(player, struct)
		return self:ConfirmTrade(player, struct)
	end)

	Server.CancelTrade.On(function(player, struct)
		return self:CancelTrade(player, struct)
	end)

	Players.PlayerRemoving:Connect(function(player)
		self:HandlePlayerLeaving(player)
	end)

	local debounce = {}

	if workspace:FindFirstChild("TradePortal") then
		workspace.TradePortal.PrimaryPart.Touched:Connect(function(hit)
			local player = game.Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(hit.Parent)
			if not player or debounce[player] then return end

			debounce[player] = true
			task.delay(1, function()
				debounce[player] = nil
			end)

			Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Transition", Arguments = {}})
			game["Teleport Service"]:Teleport(98293630968682, player)
		end)
	end

	if workspace:FindFirstChild("LobbyPortal") then
		workspace.LobbyPortal.PrimaryPart.Touched:Connect(function(hit)
			local player = game.Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(hit.Parent)
			if not player or debounce[player] then return end

			debounce[player] = true
			Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Transition", Arguments = {}})
			game["Teleport Service"]:Teleport(134765553595771, player)
			task.delay(1, function()
				debounce[player] = nil
			end)
		end)
	end

	task.spawn(function()
		while true do
			task.wait(10)
			self:CleanupExpiredTrades()
		end
	end)
end

function TradingManager:HandlePlayerLeaving(player)
	local trade = self.activeTrades[player.UserId]
	if trade then
		if trade.executionTimer then
			task.cancel(trade.executionTimer)
			trade.executionTimer = nil
		end

		local otherPlayer = trade.player1 == player and trade.player2 or trade.player1
		if otherPlayer then
			Server.UI.Fire(otherPlayer, {
				UI = "Trade", 
				Function = "CancelTrade", 
				Arguments = {CancelledBy = player.Name .. " (Disconnected)"}
			})
		end
		self.activeTrades[trade.player1.UserId] = nil
		self.activeTrades[trade.player2.UserId] = nil
	end

	for dequestKey, request in pairs(self.tradeRequests) do
		if request.sender == player or request.receiver == player then
			self.tradeRequests[dequestKey] = nil
		end
	end

	self.playerCooldowns[player.UserId] = nil
end

function TradingManager:IsPlayerOnCooldown(player)
	local cooldownEnd = self.playerCooldowns[player.UserId]
	return cooldownEnd and os.time() < cooldownEnd
end

function TradingManager:SetPlayerCooldown(player)
	self.playerCooldowns[player.UserId] = os.time() + TRADE_COOLDOWN
end

function TradingManager:SendTradeRequest(player, playerId)

	local targetPlayer = Players:GetPlayerByUserId(playerId)
	if not targetPlayer then
		for _, p in ipairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
		end
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Player not found!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end

	if targetPlayer == player then 
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Cannot trade with yourself!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end

	if self:IsPlayerOnCooldown(player) then 
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"You are on trade cooldown!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end

	local senderData = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(player, true)
	if not senderData then 
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Failed to load your data!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end

	local targetPlayerData = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(targetPlayer, true)
	if not targetPlayerData then 
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Failed to load player data!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end

	if self.activeTrades[player.UserId] then 
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"You are already in a trade!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end

	if self.activeTrades[targetPlayer.UserId] then 
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {targetPlayer.Name.." is already in a trade!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end
	
	if targetPlayerData.Settings then
	end

	if targetPlayerData.Settings and targetPlayerData.Settings.TradeInvites == false then
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"This player has trade invites disabled!", 3, "Error"}})
		return
	end
	
	Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Sent trade invite to "..targetPlayer.Name.."!", 3, "Success"}})

	local dequestKey = player.UserId .. "_" .. targetPlayer.UserId
	local reverseKey = targetPlayer.UserId .. "_" .. player.UserId

	if self.tradeRequests[dequestKey] or self.tradeRequests[reverseKey] then 
		return 
	end


	self.tradeRequests[dequestKey] = {
		sender = player,
		receiver = targetPlayer,
		timestamp = os.time()
	}

	Server.UI.Fire(targetPlayer, {
		UI = "Trade",
		Function = "DisplayTradeRequest",
		Arguments = {
			SenderName = player.Name,
			SenderId = player.UserId,
			DequestKey = dequestKey
		}
	})

	task.delay(15, function()
		self.tradeRequests[dequestKey] = nil
	end)
end

function TradingManager:RespondToTradeRequest(player, struct)
	local request = self.tradeRequests[struct.DequestKey]
	if not request or request.receiver ~= player then 
		return 
	end

	local sender = request.sender
	self.tradeRequests[struct.DequestKey] = nil

	if not struct.Accepted then 
		Server.UI.Fire(sender, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {player.Name.." declined your trade request!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end

	local senderData = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(sender, true)
	local receiverData = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(player, true)
	if not senderData or not receiverData then 
		return 
	end

	if self.activeTrades[sender.UserId] or self.activeTrades[player.UserId] then 
		return 
	end

	local tradeId = generateTradeId()
	local tradeData = {
		id = tradeId,
		player1 = sender,
		player2 = player,
		player1_units = {},
		player2_units = {},
		player1_confirmed = false,
		player2_confirmed = false,
		timestamp = os.time(),
		status = "active",
		executionTimer = nil,
		executionStartTime = nil
	}

	self.activeTrades[sender.UserId] = tradeData
	self.activeTrades[player.UserId] = tradeData

	Server.UI.Fire(sender, {
		UI = "Trade",
		Function = "StartTrade",
		Arguments = {
			TradeId = tradeId,
			PartnerName = player.Name,
			PartnerId = player.UserId
		}
	})

	Server.UI.Fire(player, {
		UI = "Trade",
		Function = "StartTrade",
		Arguments = {
			TradeId = tradeId,
			PartnerName = sender.Name,
			PartnerId = sender.UserId
		}
	})
end

function TradingManager:AddUnitsToTrade(player, struct)
	local trade = self.activeTrades[player.UserId]
	if not trade or trade.status ~= "active" then 
		return 
	end

	local playerData = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(player, true)
	if not playerData then 
		return 
	end

	local isPlayer1 = trade.player1 == player
	local currentUnits = isPlayer1 and trade.player1_units or trade.player2_units

	local currentUnitCount = 0
	for _ in pairs(currentUnits) do
		currentUnitCount = currentUnitCount + 1
	end

	if currentUnitCount + #struct.UnitIds > MAX_TRADE_UNITS then 
		Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Cannot add more than "..MAX_TRADE_UNITS.." units to trade!", 3, "Error"}})
		return 
	end

	for _, unitId in ipairs(struct.UnitIds) do
		if not isValidUnit(unitId, playerData) then
			Server.UI.Fire(player, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Invalid unit!", 3, "Error"}})
			return
		end
		currentUnits[unitId] = playerData.Inventory.Units[unitId]
	end

	trade.player1_confirmed = false
	trade.player2_confirmed = false

	if trade.executionTimer then
		task.cancel(trade.executionTimer)
		trade.executionTimer = nil
		trade.executionStartTime = nil
	end

	self:UpdateTradeDisplay(trade)
end

function TradingManager:RemoveUnitFromTrade(player, struct)
	local trade = self.activeTrades[player.UserId]
	if not trade or trade.status ~= "active" then return end

	local playerData = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(player, true)
	if not playerData then return end

	local isPlayer1 = trade.player1 == player
	local currentUnits = isPlayer1 and trade.player1_units or trade.player2_units

	local unitId = struct.UnitId
	if not unitId or not currentUnits[unitId] then return end

	currentUnits[unitId] = nil
	trade.player1_confirmed = false
	trade.player2_confirmed = false

	if trade.executionTimer then
		task.cancel(trade.executionTimer)
		trade.executionTimer = nil
		trade.executionStartTime = nil
	end

	self:UpdateTradeDisplay(trade)
end

function TradingManager:ConfirmTrade(player, struct)
	local trade = self.activeTrades[player.UserId]
	if not trade or trade.status ~= "active" then return end

	local player1Data = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(trade.player1, true)
	local player2Data = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(trade.player2, true)
	if not player1Data or not player2Data then return end

	if not validateInventorySpaceAfterTrade(player1Data, trade.player2_units, trade.player1_units)
		or not validateInventorySpaceAfterTrade(player2Data, trade.player1_units, trade.player2_units) then
		Server.UI.Fire(trade.player1, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Not enough inventory space to complete trade!", 3, "Error"}})
		Server.UI.Fire(trade.player2, {UI = "HUD", Function = "Notify", Arguments = {"Not enough inventory space to complete trade!", 3, "Error"}})
		return
	end

	local isPlayer1 = trade.player1 == player
	if isPlayer1 then
		trade.player1_confirmed = not trade.player1_confirmed
	else
		trade.player2_confirmed = not trade.player2_confirmed
	end

	if trade.executionTimer and ((isPlayer1 and not trade.player1_confirmed) or (not isPlayer1 and not trade.player2_confirmed)) then
		task.cancel(trade.executionTimer)
		trade.executionTimer = nil
		trade.executionStartTime = nil
	end

	if trade.player1_confirmed and trade.player2_confirmed and not trade.executionTimer then
		return self:StartTradeExecution(trade)
	end

	self:UpdateTradeDisplay(trade)
end

function TradingManager:StartTradeExecution(trade)
	trade.executionStartTime = os.time()
	trade.executionTimer = task.delay(TRADE_EXECUTION_DELAY, function()
		if trade.player1_confirmed and trade.player2_confirmed and trade.status == "active" then
			self:ExecuteTrade(trade)
		else
			trade.executionTimer = nil
			trade.executionStartTime = nil
		end
	end)
	self:UpdateTradeDisplay(trade)
end

function TradingManager:UpdateTradeDisplay(trade)
	local executionTimeRemaining = nil
	if trade.executionStartTime then
		executionTimeRemaining = TRADE_EXECUTION_DELAY - (os.time() - trade.executionStartTime)
	end

	Server.UI.Fire(trade.player1, {
		UI = "Trade",
		Function = "UpdateTrade",
		Arguments = {
			Player1 = trade.player1,
			Player2 = trade.player2,
			Player1Units = trade.player1_units,
			Player2Units = trade.player2_units,
			Player1Confirmed = trade.player1_confirmed,
			Player2Confirmed = trade.player2_confirmed,
			IsExecuting = trade.executionTimer ~= nil,
			ExecutionTimeRemaining = executionTimeRemaining
		}
	})

	Server.UI.Fire(trade.player2, {
		UI = "Trade",
		Function = "UpdateTrade",
		Arguments = {
			Player1 = trade.player1,
			Player2 = trade.player2,
			Player1Units = trade.player1_units,
			Player2Units = trade.player2_units,
			Player1Confirmed = trade.player1_confirmed,
			Player2Confirmed = trade.player2_confirmed,
			IsExecuting = trade.executionTimer ~= nil,
			ExecutionTimeRemaining = executionTimeRemaining
		}
	})
end

function TradingManager:ExecuteTrade(trade)
	local player1Data = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(trade.player1, true)
	local player2Data = self.game.dataManager:GetPlayerData(trade.player2, true)
	if not player1Data or not player2Data then
		self:CancelTrade(trade.player1, {})
		return
	end

	for unitId in pairs(trade.player1_units) do
		if not isValidUnit(unitId, player1Data) then
			self:CancelTrade(trade.player1, {})
			return
		end
	end
	for unitId in pairs(trade.player2_units) do
		if not isValidUnit(unitId, player2Data) then
			self:CancelTrade(trade.player1, {})
			return
		end
	end

	for unitId in pairs(trade.player1_units) do
		player1Data.Inventory.Units[unitId] = nil
	end
	for unitId in pairs(trade.player2_units) do
		player2Data.Inventory.Units[unitId] = nil
	end

	for unitId in pairs(trade.player1_units) do
		for slot, equippedUnitId in pairs(player1Data.Equipped.Units) do
			if equippedUnitId == unitId then
				player1Data.Equipped.Units[slot] = nil
			end
		end
	end
	for unitId in pairs(trade.player2_units) do
		for slot, equippedUnitId in pairs(player2Data.Equipped.Units) do
			if equippedUnitId == unitId then
				player2Data.Equipped.Units[slot] = nil
			end
		end
	end

	for _, unitData in pairs(trade.player1_units) do
		player2Data.Inventory.Units[HttpService:GenerateGUID()] = unitData
	end
	for _, unitData in pairs(trade.player2_units) do
		player1Data.Inventory.Units[HttpService:GenerateGUID()] = unitData
	end

	self.game.dataManager:UpdateData(trade.player1, "Inventory.Units", player1Data.Inventory.Units)
	self.game.dataManager:UpdateData(trade.player2, "Inventory.Units", player2Data.Inventory.Units)

	self.game.dataManager:UpdateData(trade.player1, "Equipped.Units", player1Data.Equipped.Units)
	self.game.dataManager:UpdateData(trade.player2, "Equipped.Units", player2Data.Equipped.Units)

	self.game.dataManager:AddToData(trade.player1, "Trades", 1)
	self.game.dataManager:AddToData(trade.player2, "Trades", 1)

	self:SetPlayerCooldown(trade.player1)
	self:SetPlayerCooldown(trade.player2)
	Server.UI.Fire(trade.player1, {UI = "Trade", Function = "CompleteTrade", Arguments = {Success = true, PartnerName = trade.player2.Name}})
	Server.UI.Fire(trade.player2, {UI = "Trade", Function = "CompleteTrade", Arguments = {Success = true, PartnerName = trade.player1.Name}})
	if trade.executionTimer then
		task.cancel(trade.executionTimer)
		trade.executionTimer = nil
	end
	self.activeTrades[trade.player1.UserId] = nil
	self.activeTrades[trade.player2.UserId] = nil
end

function TradingManager:CancelTrade(player, struct)
	local trade = self.activeTrades[player.UserId]
	if not trade then return end

	if trade.executionTimer then
		task.cancel(trade.executionTimer)
		trade.executionTimer = nil
	end

	Server.UI.Fire(trade.player1, {UI = "Trade", Function = "CancelTrade", Arguments = {CancelledBy = player.Name}})
	Server.UI.Fire(trade.player2, {UI = "Trade", Function = "CancelTrade", Arguments = {CancelledBy = player.Name}})

	self.activeTrades[trade.player1.UserId] = nil
	self.activeTrades[trade.player2.UserId] = nil
end

function TradingManager:CleanupExpiredTrades()
	local currentTime = os.time()
	for playerId, trade in pairs(self.activeTrades) do
		if currentTime - trade.timestamp > TRADE_TIMEOUT then
			if trade.executionTimer then
				task.cancel(trade.executionTimer)
				trade.executionTimer = nil
			end
			Server.UI.Fire(trade.player1, {UI = "Trade", Function = "CancelTrade", Arguments = {CancelledBy = "System (Timeout)"}})
			Server.UI.Fire(trade.player2, {UI = "Trade", Function = "CancelTrade", Arguments = {CancelledBy = "System (Timeout)"}})
			self.activeTrades[trade.player1.UserId] = nil
			self.activeTrades[trade.player2.UserId] = nil
		end
	end
	for dequestKey, request in pairs(self.tradeRequests) do
		if currentTime - request.timestamp > 30 then
			self.tradeRequests[dequestKey] = nil
		end
	end
end

return TradingManager

title: OIII
content:
import astropy.units as u
from astropy import constants as const
from math import *
from scipy.special import expi
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

c = const.c
a0 = const.a0
alpha = const.alpha
Ry = const.Ryd * const.h * c
k = const.k_B

def E1(x: float):
    return -expi(-x)

class Hydrogen:
    I: u.Quantity
    k: int
    q: float
    
    def __init__(self, I: u.Quantity, k: int=1):
        self.I = I
        self.k = k
        self.q = self.k
    
    def P(self, T: u.Quantity):
        beta = (self.I / T).to(1).value
        return 8 / (3 * pi * sqrt(3)) * alpha ** 4 * c / a0 * self.q * (self.I / Ry) ** 3 * E1(beta)
    
    def Ccont(self, T: u.Quantity):
        beta = (self.I / T).to(1).value
        return 8 / sqrt(pi) * alpha * pi * a0 ** 2 * c * exp(-beta) / sqrt(beta)
    
    def r(self, T: u.Quantity):
        beta = (self.I / T).to(1).value
        return 64 / (3 * sqrt(3 * pi)) * alpha ** 4 * c * pi * a0 ** 2 * beta ** (3 / 2) * exp(beta) * E1(beta)

class Metal(Hydrogen):
    z: float
    rb: float
    Arad: float
    Xrad: float
    Adi: float
    Bdi: float
    T0: float
    T1: float
    name: str
    g: int
    
    def __init__(self, I: u.Quantity, z: float, k: int, Arad: float, Xrad: float, Adi: float, Bdi: float, T0: float, T1: float, name: str, ion: bool=False):
        super().__init__(I, k)
        self.z = z
        self.q = self.k / self.z ** 2
        if ion:
            self.rb = 1
        else:
            self.rb = 2 / 3
        self.Arad = Arad
        self.Xrad = Xrad
        self.Adi = Adi
        self.Bdi = Bdi
        self.T0 = u.Quantity(T0, "K")
        self.T1 = u.Quantity(T1, "K")
        self.name = name
        if len(name) == 2:
            self.g = int(name[0]) * {'S': 1, 'P': 3, 'D': 5}[name[1]]
        else:
            self.g = int(name[2]) * 2 + 1
    
    def r(self, T: u.Quantity):
        return u.Quantity((self.rb * self.Arad * (T / u.Quantity(1e4, "K") / k) ** (-self.Xrad)).to(1).value, "cm^3/s")
    
    def d(self, T: u.Quantity):
        return u.Quantity((self.Adi / (T / u.Quantity(1, "K") / k) ** 1.5 * exp(-self.T0 * k / T) * (1 + self.Bdi * exp(-self.T1 * k / T))).to(1).value, "cm^3/s")
    
    def C(self, T: u.Quantity, omega: float):
        return u.Quantity(8.629e-6 / (T / k / u.Quantity(1, "K")).to(1).value ** 0.5 * omega / self.g, "cm^3/s")
    

kmax = 5
n = u.Quantity(10, "cm^-3")
AN = 0.0001
AO = 0.0001
Te = u.Quantity(0.7, "eV")
Ts = u.Quantity(31400, "K") * k
W = pi * (7.5 * const.R_sun / u.Quantity(3, "pc")).to(1).value ** 2

HI = [Hydrogen(Ry / i ** 2, i) for i in range(1, kmax + 1)]

ksi = (n * sum(HI[i].r(Te) for i in range(1, kmax)) / (W * HI[0].P(Ts))).to(1).value
nH = ksi * n
ne = (1 - ksi) * n

# AHI = [[u.Quantity(0, "s^-1") for l in range(j)] for j in range(kmax)] # –Ø –≤–∞–º –∑–∞–ø—Ä–µ—â–∞—é —Å–ø–æ–Ω—Ç–∞–Ω–Ω–æ –∏–∑–ª—É—á–∞—Ç—å

# AHI = [[u.Quantity(5.6e7, "s^-1") * ((HI[l].I - HI[j].I) / (HI[0].I - HI[2].I)).to(1).value ** 3 for l in range(j)] for j in range(kmax)] # –ú—ã –∂–∏–≤—ë–º –≤–æ –≤—Å–µ–ª–µ–Ω–Ω–æ–π, –≥–¥–µ —Å–∏–ª–∞ –æ—Å—Ü–∏–ª–ª—è—Ç–æ—Ä–∞ —è–≤–ª—è–µ—Ç—Å—è –º–∏—Ä–æ–≤–æ–π –∫–æ–Ω—Å—Ç–∞–Ω—Ç–æ–π (–∞ –µ—â—ë —É –∞—Ç–æ–º–∞ –≤–æ–¥–æ—Ä–æ–¥–∞ –Ω–µ—Ç –≤—ã—Ä–æ–∂–¥–µ–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö —Å–æ—Å—Ç–æ—è–Ω–∏–π –∏ –≤—Å–µ –ø–µ—Ä–µ—Ö–æ–¥—ã –¥–∏–ø–æ–ª—å–Ω–æ —Ä–∞–∑—Ä–µ—à–µ–Ω—ã)

"""
# –ö—Ä–∞–º–µ—Ä—Å —Ç–∞–∫ —Å–∫–∞–∑–∞–ª!
AHI = [[16 / (3 * pi * sqrt(3)) * alpha ** 4 * c / a0 / (j ** 3 * l * (j ** 2 - l ** 2)) for l in range(1, j )] for j in range(1, kmax + 1)]
# –ö–æ–Ω—Å—Ç–∞–Ω—Ç–∏–Ω –í–µ–Ω–∏–∞–º–∏–Ω–æ–≤–∏—á –≥–æ–≤–æ—Ä–∏–ª, —á—Ç–æ –¥–∞–Ω–Ω–∞—è —Ñ–æ—Ä–º—É–ª–∞ –¥–∞—ë—Ç 30% —Ç–æ—á–Ω–æ—Å—Ç—å. –î–ª—è –ø—Ä–æ—Å—Ç–æ—Ç—ã, —Ä–∞–∑–±—Ä–æ—Å –±—É–¥–µ–º —Å—á–∏—Ç–∞—Ç—å —Ä–∞—Å–ø—Ä–µ–¥–µ–ª—ë–Ω–Ω—ã–º –Ω–æ—Ä–º–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ.
from random import normalvariate
for i in range(len(AHI)):
    for j in range(len(AHI[i])):
        AHI[i][j] *= normalvariate(1, 0.1) # –ü—Ä–∞–≤–∏–ª–æ 3œÉ!

# """

AHI = [
    [],
    [4.70e8],
    [5.57e7, 4.41e7],
    [1.28e7, 8.42e6, 8.99e6],
    [4.12e6, 2.53e6, 2.20e6, 0],
]

nHk = [0] * kmax

for j in range(kmax - 1, 0, -1):
    nHk[j] = HI[j].r(Te)
    for l in range(j + 1, kmax):
        nHk[j] += nHk[l] * AHI[l][j]
    nHk[j] /= sum([AHI[j][l] for l in range(j)])

for j in range(1, len(nHk)):
    nHk[j] *= ne * nH

nHk[0] = nH

IHalpha = (HI[1].I - HI[2].I) * AHI[2][1] * nHk[2]
IHbeta = (HI[1].I - HI[3].I) * AHI[3][1] * nHk[3]

print(f"Behold Balmer's decrement: {(IHalpha / IHbeta).to(1).value}")

NIIOmega = {
    ("3P0", "1D"): 2.68,
    ("3P1", "1D"): 2.68,
    ("3P2", "1D"): 2.68,
    ("3P0", "1S"): 0.35,
    ("3P1", "1S"): 0.35,
    ("3P2", "1S"): 0.35,
    ("1D", "1S"): 0.41,
    ("3P0", "3P1"): 0.40,
    ("3P0", "3P2"): 0.28,
    ("3P1", "3P2"): 1.13,
}

NIIA = {
    ("1D", "1S"): 1.1,
    ("3P2", "1S"): 1.5e-4,
    ("3P1", "1S"): 3.4e-2,
    ("3P2", "1D"): 3.0e-3,
    ("3P1", "1D"): 1.0e-3,
    ("3P0", "1D"): 5.4e-7,
    ("3P1", "3P2"): 7.5e-6,
    ("3P0", "3P2"): 1.2e-12,
    ("3P0", "3P1"): 2.1e-6,
}

NIIA1 = 9.84e-4
NIIA2 = 2.91e-3
NIIE1 = u.Quantity(1.900 - 0.006, "eV")
NIIE2 = u.Quantity(1.900 - 0.016, "eV")

NIIlevels = {
    "3P": u.Quantity(48.7, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "1D": u.Quantity(15316.2, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "1S": u.Quantity(32688.8, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "5S": u.Quantity(46784.6, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "3P0": u.Quantity(0, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "3P1": u.Quantity(48.7, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "3P2": u.Quantity(130.8, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
}

NI = [14.53413, 29.60125, 47.4453, 77.4735, 97.8901, 552.06741, 667.0461377]
NI = [u.Quantity(i, "eV") for i in NI]

N = [
    [4.10e-13, 6.08e-1, 2.98e-3, 0, 2.20e5, 0],
    [2.20e-12, 6.39e-1, 7.41e-3, 7.64e-2, 2.01e5, 7.37e4],
    [5.00e-12, 6.76e-1, 1.13e-2, 1.64e-2, 1.72e5, 2.25e5],
    [6.50e-12, 7.43e-1, 2.62e-3, 2.43e-2, 1.02e5, 1.25e5],
    [1.50e-11, 8.50e-1, 7.50e-2, 3.50e-1, 4.75e6, 8.35e5],
    [2.90e-11, 7.50e-1, 4.61e-2, 3.09e-1, 5.44e6, 1.14e6],
    [2.00e-11, 7.26e-1, 0, 0, 0, 0],
]

OIIIOmega = {
    ("3P0", "1D"): 2.17,
    ("3P1", "1D"): 2.17,
    ("3P2", "1D"): 2.17,
    ("3P0", "1S"): 0.28,
    ("3P1", "1S"): 0.28,
    ("3P2", "1S"): 0.28,
    ("1D", "1S"): 0.62,
    ("3P0", "3P1"): 0.54,
    ("3P0", "3P2"): 0.27,
    ("3P1", "3P2"): 1.29,
}

OIIIA = {
    ("1D", "1S"): 1.8,
    ("3P2", "1S"): 7.8e-4,
    ("3P1", "1S"): 2.2e-1,
    ("3P2", "1D"): 2.0e-2,
    ("3P1", "1D"): 6.7e-3,
    ("3P0", "1D"): 2.7e-6,
    ("3P1", "3P2"): 9.8e-5,
    ("3P0", "3P2"): 3.0e-11,
    ("3P0", "3P1"): 2.6e-5,
}

OIIIA1 = 6.21e-3
OIIIA2 = 1.18e-2
OIIIE1 = u.Quantity(2.514 - 0.014, "eV")
OIIIE2 = u.Quantity(2.514 - 0.038, "eV")

O = [
    [3.10e-13, 6.78e-1, 1.11e-3, 9.25e-2, 1.75e5, 1.45e5],
    [2.00e-12, 6.46e-1, 5.07e-3, 1.81e-1, 1.98e5, 3.35e5],
    [5.10e-12, 6.60e-1, 1.48e-2, 3.05e-1, 2.41e5, 2.83e5],
    [9.60e-12, 6.70e-1, 1.84e-2, 1.00e-1, 2.12e5, 2.83e5],
    [1.20e-11, 7.79e-1, 4.13e-3, 1.62e-1, 1.25e5, 2.27e5],
    [2.30e-11, 8.02e-1, 1.06e-1, 3.40e-1, 6.25e6, 1.12e6],
    [4.10e-11, 7.42e-1, 6.23e-2, 3.04e-1, 7.01e6, 1.47e6],
    [2.62e-11, 7.26e-1, 0, 0, 0, 0],
    
]

OI = [13.618055, 35.12112, 54.93554, 77.41350, 113.8990, 138.1189, 739.32697, 871.4099138]
OI = [u.Quantity(i, "eV") for i in OI]

OIIIlevels = {
    "3P": u.Quantity(113.178, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "1D": u.Quantity(20273.27, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "1S": u.Quantity(43185.74 , "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "5S": u.Quantity(60324.79, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "3P0": u.Quantity(0, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "3P1": u.Quantity(113.178, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
    "3P2": u.Quantity(306.174, "cm^-1") * const.h * c,
}

def fillOmega(omega, states, T):
    newomega = dict(omega)
    for key in omega:
        l, u = key
        if l in states and u in states:
            newomega[(u, l)] = omega[key] * states[u].g / states[l].g * exp(((states[u].I - states[l].I) / T).to(1).value)
    return newomega

def processMetal(omega, A, A1, A2, E1, E2, El, I, state, ionnum, n0, ne, Te, Ts, W, levels):
    sec = u.Quantity(1, "s")
    cm3 = u.Quantity(1, "cm^3")
    system = np.zeros((ionnum, ionnum), dtype=float)
    b = np.zeros((ionnum,), dtype=float)
    M = []
    for i in range(ionnum):
        Arad, Xrad, Adi, Bdi, T0, T1 = El[i]
        M.append(Metal(I[i], sqrt(I[i + 1] / I[i]), 1, Arad, Xrad, Adi, Bdi, T0, T1, "1S", i != 0))
    for k in range(ionnum):
        if k < ionnum - 1:
            system[k, k] -= ((M[k].Ccont(Te) * ne + W * M[k].P(Ts)) * sec).to(1).value
            system[k + 1, k] += ((M[k].Ccont(Te) * ne + W * M[k].P(Ts)) * sec).to(1).value
        if k > 0:
            system[k, k] -= ((ne * (M[k].r(Te) + M[k].d(Te))) * sec).to(1).value
            system[k - 1, k] += ((ne * (M[k].r(Te) + M[k].d(Te))) * sec).to(1).value
    for k in range(ionnum):
        system[-1, k] = 1
    b[-1] = (n0 * cm3).to(1).value
    nM = np.linalg.solve(system, b)[state]
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.plot(np.linalg.solve(system, b))
    ax.set_yscale("log")
    plt.show()
    def calc(n, chosenStates, omega, El, state, levels, I, ne, Te):
        prestat = set()
        for key in omega:
            prestat.add(key[0])
            prestat.add(key[1])
        stat = set()
        for key in prestat:
            if key in chosenStates:
                stat.add(key)
        states = {}
        Arad, Xrad, Adi, Bdi, T0, T1 = El[state]
        for key in stat:
            states[key] = Metal(levels[key], sqrt(I[state + 1] / I[state]), 1, Arad, Xrad, Adi, Bdi, T0, T1, key, state != 0)
        omega = fillOmega(omega, states, Te)
        stat = {}
        num = 0
        for key in states:
            stat[key] = num
            num-=-1
        system = np.zeros((num, num), dtype=float)
        b = np.zeros((num, ), dtype=float)
        for pair in omega:
            l, u = pair # to, from
            if l in stat and u in stat:
                system[stat[l], stat[u]] += (states[u].C(Te, omega[pair]) * ne * sec).to(1).value
                system[stat[u], stat[u]] -= (states[u].C(Te, omega[pair]) * ne * sec).to(1).value
                if pair in A:
                    system[stat[l], stat[u]] += A[pair]
                    system[stat[u], stat[u]] -= A[pair]
        for i in range(num):
            system[-1, i] = 1
        b[-1] = n
        return np.linalg.solve(system, b), stat
    sys, stat = calc(nM, {"3P0", "3P1", "3P2", "1D", "1S"}, omega, El, state, levels, I, ne, Te)
    # sys, stat = calc(nM, {"3P1", "1D", "1S"}, omega, El, state, levels, I, ne, Te)
    return sys[stat["1D"]] * A1 * E1 / cm3 / sec + sys[stat["1D"]] * A2 * E2 / cm3 / sec

NII = processMetal(NIIOmega, NIIA, NIIA1, NIIA2, NIIE1, NIIE2, N, NI, 1, 6, n * AN, ne, Te, Ts, W, NIIlevels)
OIII = processMetal(OIIIOmega, OIIIA, OIIIA1, OIIIA2, OIIIE1, OIIIE2, O, OI, 2, 7, n * AO, ne, Te, Ts, W, OIIIlevels)

print(f"OIII / Halpha: {(OIII / IHalpha).to(1).value}")
print(f"NII / Hbeta: {(NII / IHbeta).to(1).value}")

T‚Äée‚Äés‚Äét‚Äé ‚Äéc‚Äéo‚Äém‚Äép‚Äél‚Äée‚Äét‚Äée‚Äé.‚Äé

J‚Äéu‚Äés‚Äét‚Äé ‚Äés‚Äéo‚Äé ‚Äéy‚Äéo‚Äéu‚Äé ‚Äék‚Äén‚Äéo‚Äéw‚Äé,‚Äé ‚ÄéI‚Äé ‚Äéd‚Äéo‚Äé ‚Äét‚Äéh‚Äéi‚Äés‚Äé ‚Äéc‚Äér‚Äéa‚Äép‚Äé ‚Äée‚Äév‚Äée‚Äér‚Äé ‚Äéd‚Äéa‚Äéy‚Äé ‚Äés‚Äéo‚Äé ‚Äéd‚Äéo‚Äén‚Äé'‚Äét‚Äé ‚Äég‚Äéi‚Äév‚Äée‚Äé ‚Äém‚Äée‚Äé ‚Äéa‚Äé ‚Äéh‚Äéa‚Äér‚Äéd‚Äé ‚Äét‚Äéi‚Äém‚Äée‚Äé.‚Äé

title: dril.lua
content:
local rs_output = {}
rs_output.__index = rs_output

function rs_output:new(side)
	local object_table = {side = side}
	setmetatable(object_table, self)
	return object_table
end



function rs_output:enable()
print(self.side, "enable")
	rs.setOutput(self.side ,true)
end



function rs_output:disable()
print(self.side, "disable")
	rs.setOutput(self.side ,false)
end



function rs_output:get_input()
	return rs.getInput(self.side)
end




local gearshift = rs_output:new("right")
local sticker = rs_output:new("top")


sticker:enable()
sleep(0.2)
sticker:disable()
gearshift:enable()
sleep(10)
gearshift:disable()

-----PREFERENCES/VARIABLES-----
local pin = 1528
local maxtries = 3
local locktime = 60 --seconds
local waittotry = 3 --seconds
local redstoneSide = "left"
local modemSide = "top"
local remoteMonitorName = "monitor_0" -- nome do monitor remoto na rede

local tries = 0
local input = ""
local keypad = {
  {1,2,4},
  {2,7,4},
  {3,12,4},
  {4,2,6},
  {5,7,6},
  {6,12,6},
  {7,2,8},
  {8,7,8},
  {9,12,8},
  {0,7,10}
}

-----FUNCTIONS-----
function checkClick(t,x,y)
  for i,v in pairs(t) do
    local num,cx,cy = unpack(v)
    if (x >= cx) and (x <= cx + 2) and (y == cy) then
      return true,num
    end
  end
  return false
end

function numClick(num)
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setCursorPos", (5 + (string.len(input) * 2)), 2)
  input = input .. num
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "write", "*")

  if (string.len(input) == 4) then
    if (tostring(pin) == input) then
      monAction("Access Granted")
      doorOpen()
      monReset(true)
      input = ""
      tries = 0
    else
      input = ""
      tries = tries + 1
      if (tries >= maxtries) then
        monReset()
        peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setBackgroundColor", colors.red)
        monAction("TERMINAL LOCKED")
        sleep(locktime)
        os.reboot()
      end
      monAction("Access Denied")
      sleep(waittotry)
      monReset(true)
    end
  end
end

function monAction(mess)
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setCursorPos", 1, 1)
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "clearLine")
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "write", mess)
end

function monReset(isClear)
  if (isClear) then peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "clearLine") end
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setCursorPos", 5, 2)
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "write", "_ _ _ _")
end

function doorOpen()
  redstone.setOutput(redstoneSide, true)
  sleep(3)
  redstone.setOutput(redstoneSide, false)
end

-----BEGIN MAIN-----
local modem = peripheral.wrap(modemSide)
if not modem then error("Modem n?o encontrado!") end

-- Ativar rede de perif?ricos
modem.open(0)
print("Conectando ao monitor remoto...")

-- Espera o monitor remoto aparecer
while not peripheral.isPresent(remoteMonitorName) do
  print("Aguardando monitor remoto...")
  sleep(2)
end

peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setTextScale", 0.5)
peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setBackgroundColor", colors.red)
peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setTextColor", colors.black)
peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "clear")

for i,v in pairs(keypad) do
  local num,x,y = unpack(v)
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setCursorPos", x, y)
  peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "write", " " .. num .. " ")
end

peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setBackgroundColor", colors.black)
peripheral.call(remoteMonitorName, "setTextColor", colors.white)
monReset()

print("Sistema iniciado com monitor remoto via modem.")

while true do
  local event, side, x, y = os.pullEvent("monitor_touch")
  validClick,num = checkClick(keypad,x,y)
  if (validClick) then
    numClick(num)
  end
end

-- controller.lua
-- Steuert das Startsignal f√ºr alle Musik-Computer
-- Version 1.0

local CONTROL_FILE = "disk/control.txt"
local TRIGGER_SIDE = "back"  -- <--- Seite hier anpassen (z.B. "left", "right", "back" usw.)

-- -----------------------------
-- Hilfsfunktion: schreibt die Control-Datei
-- -----------------------------
local function writeControl(play, startTime)
    local f = fs.open(CONTROL_FILE, "w")
    f.writeLine("play=" .. tostring(play))
    f.writeLine("startTime=" .. tostring(startTime))
    f.close()
end

-- -----------------------------
-- Hauptschleife
-- -----------------------------
print("Musikcontroller aktiv.")
print("Warte auf Redstone-Signal an Seite: " .. TRIGGER_SIDE)

-- Sicherstellen, dass Datei existiert
writeControl(false, 0)

while true do
    -- Auf steigende Flanke warten (Signal AN)
    if redstone.getInput(TRIGGER_SIDE) then
        local startTime = os.epoch("utc") + 1000 -- Start in 1 Sekunde
        print("Signal erkannt! Starte alle Ger√§te in 1 Sekunde...")
        writeControl(true, startTime)

        -- 2 Sekunden warten, damit alle Ger√§te starten
        sleep(2)

        -- Dann Signal zur√ºcksetzen
        writeControl(false, startTime)
        print("Startsignal beendet. Warte auf n√§chstes Signal.")

        -- Warten bis das Signal wieder aus ist (Flankenerkennung)
        while redstone.getInput(TRIGGER_SIDE) do
            sleep(0.1)
        end
    end

    sleep(0.1)
end

title: Notes
content:
-- Musikcomputer.lua
-- CC:Tweaked Musiksystem (mit BPM, Filterung & synchronisiertem Start)
-- Version 2.0

local CONFIG_FILE = "config.txt"
local CONTROL_FILE = "disk/control.txt"
local SONG_PATH_PREFIX = "disk/song_"
local instrumentConfig = {}

-- -----------------------------
-- Hilfsfunktionen
-- -----------------------------
local function fileExists(path)
    local f = fs.open(path, "r")
    if f then f.close() return true else return false end
end

local function saveConfig(config)
    local f = fs.open(CONFIG_FILE, "w")
    for k, v in pairs(config) do
        f.writeLine(k .. "=" .. v)
    end
    f.close()
end

local function loadConfig()
    local config = {}
    local f = fs.open(CONFIG_FILE, "r")
    if not f then return nil end
    for line in f.readLine do
        local key, value = line:match("^(.-)=(.*)$")
        if key and value then
            config[key] = value
        end
    end
    f.close()
    return config
end

-- -----------------------------
-- Initialisierung
-- -----------------------------
local function initialize()
    print("Keine Konfiguration gefunden. Initialisierung startet...")
    local config = {}

    write("Instrumentname: ")
    config.name = read()

    local sides = {"front", "right", "back", "left"}
    for _, side in ipairs(sides) do
        write("Ton an Seite '" .. side .. "' (z.B. C#2 oder none): ")
        config[side] = read()
    end

    saveConfig(config)
    print("Konfiguration gespeichert.")
    return config
end

-- -----------------------------
-- Lied laden (inkl. BPM)
-- -----------------------------
local function loadSong(instrumentName)
    local songPath = SONG_PATH_PREFIX .. instrumentName .. ".txt"
    if not fs.exists(songPath) then
        error("Songdatei nicht gefunden: " .. songPath)
    end

    local f = fs.open(songPath, "r")
    local bpm = 120
    local notes = {}

    while true do
        local line = f.readLine()
        if not line then break end

        if line:match("^BPM=") then
            bpm = tonumber(line:match("BPM=(%d+)"))
        elseif not (line:match("^#") or line == "") then
            local tonePart, length = line:match("^(.-)|(%d+)$")
            if tonePart and length then
                local tones = {}
                for tone in string.gmatch(tonePart, "([^,]+)") do
                    table.insert(tones, tone)
                end
                table.insert(notes, {tones = tones, length = tonumber(length)})
            end
        end
    end
    f.close()
    return bpm, notes
end

-- -----------------------------
-- Filter nach bespielbaren Noten
-- -----------------------------
local function filterSong(song, config, bpm)
    local playable = {}
    local sideNotes = {}
    for _, side in ipairs({"front", "right", "back", "left"}) do
        if config[side] and config[side] ~= "none" then
            sideNotes[config[side]] = side
        end
    end

    local function noteLengthToSeconds(noteValue, bpm)
        return (4 / noteValue) * (60 / bpm)
    end

    for _, entry in ipairs(song) do
        local validTones = {}
        for _, tone in ipairs(entry.tones) do
            if sideNotes[tone] then
                table.insert(validTones, tone)
            end
        end

        if #validTones > 0 then
            table.insert(playable, {
                tones = validTones,
                length = noteLengthToSeconds(entry.length, bpm)
            })
        else
            table.insert(playable, {
                tones = {"REST"},
                length = noteLengthToSeconds(entry.length, bpm)
            })
        end
    end

    return playable, sideNotes
end

-- -----------------------------
-- Steuerdatei lesen
-- -----------------------------
local function readControlFile()
    if not fileExists(CONTROL_FILE) then return false, 0 end

    local f = fs.open(CONTROL_FILE, "r")
    local play = false
    local startTime = 0

    while true do
        local line = f.readLine()
        if not line then break end
        local key, val = line:match("^(.-)=(.*)$")
        if key == "play" then
            play = (val == "true")
        elseif key == "startTime" then
            startTime = tonumber(val)
        end
    end
    f.close()
    return play, startTime
end

-- -----------------------------
-- Song abspielen
-- -----------------------------
local function playSong(filtered, sideNotes)
    for _, entry in ipairs(filtered) do
        if entry.tones[1] == "REST" then
            sleep(entry.length)
        else
            -- Redstone aktivieren
            for _, tone in ipairs(entry.tones) do
                local side = sideNotes[tone]
                if side then redstone.setOutput(side, true) end
            end

            sleep(0.001)

            -- Redstone deaktivieren
            for _, tone in ipairs(entry.tones) do
                local side = sideNotes[tone]
                if side then redstone.setOutput(side, false) end
            end

            -- Rest der Notenl√§nge warten
            local remaining = entry.length - 0.001
            if remaining > 0 then sleep(remaining) end
        end
    end
end

-- -----------------------------
-- Hauptprogramm
-- -----------------------------
if fileExists(CONFIG_FILE) then
    instrumentConfig = loadConfig()
    print("Konfiguration geladen f√ºr Instrument: " .. instrumentConfig.name)
else
    instrumentConfig = initialize()
end

print("Lade Song von Disk...")
local bpm, song = loadSong(instrumentConfig.name)
print("Song geladen (" .. #song .. " Schritte) mit BPM = " .. bpm)

print("Filtere Song f√ºr bespielbare Noten...")
local filtered, sideNotes = filterSong(song, instrumentConfig, bpm)
print("Gefilterter Song enth√§lt " .. #filtered .. " Eintr√§ge.")

print("Warte auf Startsignal...")

while true do
    local play, startTime = readControlFile()
    if play then
        local current = os.epoch("utc")
        local diff = startTime - current
        if diff > 0 then
            print("Starte Song in " .. string.format("%.2f", diff / 1000) .. " Sekunden...")
            sleep(diff / 1000)
        end

        print("Starte Abspielen!")
        playSong(filtered, sideNotes)
        print("Song beendet.")
        break
    end

    sleep(0.2) -- Systemschonende Abfrage
end

monitor = peripheral.wrap("monitor_1")
function pos(...) return term.setCursorPos(...) end
function cls(...) return term.clear() end
function tCol(...) return term.setTextColor(...) end
function bCol(...) return term.setBackgroundColor(...) end
function box(...) return paintutils.drawFilledBox(...) end
function line(...) return paintutils.drawLine(...) end
function write(...) return term.write(...) end
term.redirect(monitor)
w, h = monitor.getSize()

function getSize() w,h = monitor.getSize() end
tCol(colors.white)
local darkmode = true
local darkmodec

local boolArray = {false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false,false}

local function brf2()
    monitor.setTextScale(1.5)
    getSize()
    cls()
    if darkmode then darkmodec = colours.black else darkmodec = colours.blue end
    box(1,1,w,h,darkmodec)
    pos(w/2-#"BRF2"/2,1)
    write("BRF2")

    -- left column (6)
    local y=3
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Shimmer Dust") if boolArray[1]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Certus Quartz") if boolArray[2]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Certus Quartz Dust") if boolArray[3]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Shimmer") if boolArray[4]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Amethyst Dust") if boolArray[5]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Glow Ink Sac") if boolArray[6]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Ink Sac") if boolArray[7]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Paper") if boolArray[8]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    pos(5,y) bCol(darkmodec) write("Clay Dust") if boolArray[9]==false then box(23,y,26,y,colors.red) else box(23,y,26,y,colors.lime) end; y=y+2
    -- right column (5)
    local y2=3
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Lime Dust") if boolArray[10]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end; y2=y2+2
    pos(28,y2) bCol(darkmodec) write("Dried Kelp") if boolArray[11]==false then box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.red) else box(46,y2,49,y2,colors.lime) end

    pos(1,h) bCol(colors.black) write("EXIT")
    while true do
        local event, button, mx, my = os.pullEvent()
        if event == "monitor_touch" then
            if mx >= 1 and mx <= (1+#"EXIT") and my == h then return "menu" end
            local ly=3
            for i=1,9 do if mx>=23 and mx<=26 and my==ly then boolArray[i]=not boolArray[i]; brf2() end; ly=ly+2 end
            local ry=3
            for i=10,11 do if mx>=46 and mx<=49 and my==ry then boolArray[i]=not boolArray[i]; brf2() end; ry=ry+2 end
            if mx >= w/2-#"BRF2"/2 and mx <= w/2+#"BRF2"/2 and my == 1 then darkmode = not darkmode; brf2() end
        end
    end
end

return {brf2 = brf2}

        end
    end
end

return {electronics = electronics}

monitor = peripheral.wrap("monitor_1")
function pos(...) return term.setCursorPos(...) end
function cls(...) return term.clear() end
function tCol(...) return term.setTextColor(...) end
function bCol(...) return term.setBackgroundColor(...) end
function box(...) return paintutils.drawFilledBox(...) end
function line(...) return paintutils.drawLine(...) end
function write(...) return term.write(...) end
term.redirect(monitor)
w, h = monitor.getSize()
local foundrya = require("foundry")
local dyea = require("dye")
local blocksa = require("blocks")
local loga = require("log")
local basicsa = require("basics")
--local brf1a = require("brf1")
local nethera = require("nether")
local electronicsa = require("electronics")
local brf2a = require("brf2")


function getSize() w,h = monitor.getSize() end
tCol(colors.white)
local andes = false
local darkmode = true
local darkmodec
------------------------------------------------------------

function drawMenu()
    monitor.setTextScale(2)
    getSize()
    bCol(colors.blue)
    if darkmode then
        box(1,1,w,h,colors.blue)
    else
        box(1,1,w,h,colors.blue)
    end
    
    pos(w/2-#"MENU"/2,1)
    write("MENU")

    monitor.setBackgroundColor(colors.lightGray)
    pos(5,3)
    write("FOUNDRY")
    pos(5,6)
    write("DYE")
    pos(5,9)
    write("BLOCKS")
    pos(5,12)
    write("LOG")
    pos(5,15)
    write("BASICS")
    pos(w/2,3)
    write("BRF1")
    pos(w/2,6)
    write("NETHER")
    pos(w/2,9)
    write("ELECTRONICS")
    pos(w/2,12)
    write("BRF2")
    pos(w/2,15)
    write("IRF")
    pos(1,17)
    bCol(colors.black)
    write("EXIT")
    bCol(colors.blue)

end

function main()
    drawMenu()
    
    while true do
    
        local event, button, mx, my = os.pullEvent()
        if event == "monitor_touch" then
        
            if mx >= 5 and mx <= (5+#"FOUNDRY") and my == 3 then
                foundrya.foundry()
                if foundrya.foundry() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end
            if mx >= 5 and mx <= (5+#"DYE") and my == 6 then
                dyea.dye()
                if dyea.dye() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end
            if mx >= 5 and mx <= (5+#"BLOCKS") and my == 9 then
                blocksa.blocks()
                if blocksa.blocks() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end
            if mx >= 5 and mx <= (5+#"LOG") and my == 12 then
                loga.log()
                if loga.log() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end
            if mx >= 5 and mx <= (5+#"BASICS") and my == 15 then
                basicsa.basics()
                if basicsa.basics() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end
           --[[ if mx >= w/2 and mx <= (w/2+#"BRF1") and my == 3 then
                brf1a.brf1()
                if brf1a.brf1() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end--]]
            if mx >= w/2 and mx <= (w/2+#"NETHER") and my == 6 then
                nethera.nether()
                if nethera.nether() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end
            if mx >= w/2 and mx <= (w/2+#"ELECTRONICS") and my == 9 then
                electronicsa.electronics()
                if electronicsa.electronics() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end
            if mx >= w/2 and mx <= (w/2+#"BRF2") and my == 12 then
                brf2a.brf2()
                if brf2a.brf2() == "menu" then
                    drawMenu()
                end
            end
            
        end
    end 
end

--------------------------------------------------------------

main()
return {main = main}

local reactorName = "BiggerReactors_Reactor_1"
local maxTemp = 2200
local minTemp = 1800

local turbineName = "BiggerReactors_Turbine_0"
local targetRPM = 1800
local stepSize = 10

local checkInterval = 0.1
 
local mon = peripheral.wrap("monitor_2")
term.redirect(mon)
 
local reactor = peripheral.wrap(reactorName)
if not reactor then
  error("Reactor not found: " .. reactorName)
end
 
local turbine = peripheral.wrap(turbineName)
if not turbine then
  error("Turbine not found: " .. turbineName)
end
 
while true do
  local rodPercent = 100 * math.max(reactor.getCasingTemperature() - minTemp, 0) / (maxTemp - minTemp)
  reactor.setAllControlRodLevels(rodPercent)
  
  local rpm = turbine.rotor().RPM()
  
  if rpm > targetRPM then
	turbine.fluidTank().setNominalFlowRate(turbine.fluidTank().nominalFlowRate() - stepSize)
  else
	turbine.fluidTank().setNominalFlowRate(turbine.fluidTank().nominalFlowRate() + stepSize)
  end  
  
  if turbine.battery().stored() / turbine.battery().capacity() < 0.2 then
    if not reactor.active() then
      reactor.setActive(true)
      print("Reactor ON")
    end
  elseif turbine.battery().stored() / turbine.battery().capacity() > 0.8 then
    if reactor.active() then
      reactor.setActive(false)
      print("Reactor OFF")
    end
  end
  
  term.clear()
  term.setCursorPos(1,1)
  
  print("Temperature: " .. math.floor(reactor.fuelTemperature()))
  print("Rods: " .. math.floor(reactor.getControlRod(0).level()))
  sleep(checkInterval)
end

local RS = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage")
local rebirth = RS:WaitForChild("RequestCompletionRebirth")

local maps = workspace.Maps
local mapId = 1
local found = maps and maps:FindFirstChild("Map"..mapId)
local burger = found and found.burger

local plr = game.Players.LocalPlayer

local stopped = false

local function re(h)
    if h then 
        h.Health = 0 
    end
end

plr.Chatted:Connect(function(msg)
    if msg == "StopInit" then 
        stopped = true 
    end
end)

while true do
    if stopped then 
        break 
    end
    local character = plr.Character or plr.CharacterAdded:Wait() 
    if character and burger then
        local humanoid = character:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid") 
        character:PivotTo(burger:GetPivot())
        wait(0.5)
        local proximity = burger:FindFirstChild("ProximityPrompt")
        if proximity then
            proximity:InputHoldBegin()
            local triggered = false
            proximity.Triggered:Connect(function() 
                triggered = true 
            end)   
            local startTime = tick()
            while not triggered and (tick() - startTime) < 1 do
                wait(0.1)
            end
            if triggered then
                wait(1)
                rebirth:FireServer()
                wait(3)
            else
                re(humanoid)
                wait(5)
            end
        else
            re(humanoid)
            wait(5)
        end
    else
        re(humanoid)
        wait(5)
    end
end

import sys
from PIL import Image

def convert_to_grayscale_bmp(input_path, output_path):
    img = Image.open(input_path)
    grayscale_img = img.convert('L')
    grayscale_img.save(output_path, 'BMP')

input_file = sys.argv[1]
output_file = input_file.strip(".jpg") + ".bmp"

convert_to_grayscale_bmp(input_file, output_file)

title: Turbine control 2
content:
-- Peripheral setup
local modem = peripheral.find("modem") or error("No modem found", 0)
local monitor = peripheral.wrap("front") or error("No monitor on front", 0)

-- Monitor setup
monitor.setTextScale(0.5)
monitor.setBackgroundColor(colors.cyan)
monitor.clear()

local function drawLabel(y, text)
    monitor.setCursorPos(1, y)
    monitor.clearLine()
    monitor.write(text)
end

local function drawUI()
    drawLabel(4, "Fuel Feed")
    drawLabel(5, "-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-")
    drawLabel(8, "Clutch")
    drawLabel(9, "-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-")
    drawLabel(12, "Output")
    drawLabel(13, "-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-")
    monitor.setCursorPos(4, 1)
    monitor.write("Turbine #1")
end

drawUI()

term.clear()
term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
print("Running...")

-- Core Functions
local function transmitAndDisplay(channelOut, channelIn, mode, yPos, bgColor, side, pulse)
    if side then rs.setOutput(side, true) end
    modem.transmit(channelOut, channelIn, mode)
    monitor.setCursorPos(1, yPos)
    monitor.clearLine()
    monitor.blit(mode, ("0"):rep(#mode), bgColor)
    if pulse then sleep(1); if side then rs.setOutput(side, false) end end
end

local function fuelFeed(side, mode, bgColor)
    transmitAndDisplay(3, 4, mode, 6, bgColor, side, true)
end

local function shift(side, mode, bgColor)
    rs.setOutput("left", false)
    transmitAndDisplay(2, 3, mode, 10, bgColor, side, false)
end

local function modemCall(channel, callback)
    modem.open(channel)
    local _, _, _, _, message = os.pullEvent("modem_message")
    modem.close(channel)
    if callback then callback(message) end
    return message
end

local function battCall()
    return tonumber(modemCall(4, function(msg)
        term.setCursorPos(1, 2)
        term.clearLine()
        print(msg)
    end)) or 0
end

local function outputCall()
    modemCall(5, function(msg)
        monitor.setCursorPos(1, 14)
        monitor.clearLine()
        monitor.write(msg)
    end)
end

-- Main control loop
local inject, delay = 0, 0

while not rs.getInput("front") do
    local batt = battCall()
    local speed = rs.getAnalogInput("right")

    outputCall()

    if inject == 1 then delay = delay + 1 end
    if delay >= 280 then inject, delay = 0, 0 end

    if speed == 0 then
        shift("top", "Offline", "eeeeeee")
        if batt <= 30 and inject == 0 then
            fuelFeed("bottom", "Engaged", "ddddddd")
            inject = 1
        elseif batt >= 35 then
            fuelFeed("top", "Offline", "eeeeeee")
        end
    elseif speed <= 8 then
        shift("top", "Low RPM", "1111111")
        if batt >= 35 then
            fuelFeed("top", "Offline", "eeeeeee")
        end
    else
        shift("left", "Engaged", "ddddddd")
        if batt >= 35 then
            fuelFeed("top", "Offline", "eeeeeee")
        end
    end
end
